<bibRefCitation author="Budha, PB" journalOrPublisher="ZooKeys" pageId="14" pageNumber="143" pagination="1 - 48" title="Annotated checklist of terrestrial gastropods of Nepal." url="http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.492.9175" volume="392" year="2015">Budha et al. 2015</bibRefCitation>
